OL,4,G0400FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,5,     GThe staff of Globelink News are
OL,6,     Gto be the stars of a docusoap,
OL,7,     Gwhether they like it or not. As
OL,8,     Gthey fend off hand-held cameras,
OL,9,     Gthey discover their futures are
OL,10,     Gin doubt.
OL,11,G0430FStereo Underground
OL,12,     GRichard Latto presents
OL,13,     Galternative anthems from a music
OL,14,     Gcommunity with attitude. S10EP08
OL,15,G0530FJack Hargreaves' Old Country
OL,16,     GJack goes rabbiting with nets,
OL,17,     Gthe way it has been done for over
OL,18,     G800 years. He describes what the
OL,19,     Gvisitor should look for on a trip
OL,20,     Gto the countryside.
